        "description": "<p>This plugin lets you infinity scroll your Woocommerce products to your WordPress site.</p>\n",
        "installation": "<ol>\n<li>Download the plugin.</li>\n<li>Activate the plugin in the WordPress Admin Panel.</li>\n<li>\n<p>Usage of the plugin:</p>\n<p>Shortcode: &#8220;[shopizi selector=&#8221;my_products&#8221; category=&#8221;laptops&#8221; method=&#8221;post&#8221; action=&#8221;shopizi&#8221; post_type=&#8221;product&#8221; ppp=&#8221;5&#8243; order=&#8221;DESC&#8221;]</p>\n<p>or in php place do_shortcode(&#8216;[shopizi selector=&#8221;my_products&#8221; category=&#8221;laptops&#8221; method=&#8221;post&#8221; action=&#8221;shopizi&#8221; post_type=&#8221;product&#8221; ppp=&#8221;5&#8243; order=&#8221;DESC&#8221;]&#8217;)&#8221;.</p>\n<p>The &#8220;selector&#8221; is ID of the your DOM element.</p>\n<p>NO NEED  functions.php !</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n",
        "faq": "<p>There are currently no FAQs at this time.</p>\n",
